Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.99,Location,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\an8}Nice\N(South France)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbara, how would you like a Moscow Mule?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Fritz, I've brought you some juice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fritz, say thank you to your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fritz!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll gradually warm up to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,just like how I'll have to get\Nused to this new art business.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all just so sudden for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to live in this wonderful mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.51,0:00:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,having such a kind husband\Nto make me delicious cocktails...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.31,0:00:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you feel anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.23,0:00:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:00:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,From the neighbor's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like we were being watched from\Nthe second-floor window over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that there's no one living there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, I heard from Mrs. d'Autrey...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The neighbors, the husband and wife,\Nwere killed twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, ghosts appear in that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Michael?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you believe that crazy story!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want us to go out, just as\Na family, every once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need a bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That way, Fritz will\Nwarm up to you faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. That's what I'm aiming for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.71,0:01:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Mr. Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:39.36,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,500)\pos(360,340)}Happy Holidays
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the results of your investigation, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start with Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.29,0:03:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The police are after him because he's a suspect\Nfor the murder of a married couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but there hasn't been any trace of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was called back by the\Npolice, this is what Tenma said:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A boy whose life he saved ten years ago\Nkilled three people and escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The victims included the director\Nof Eisler Memorial Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy's name was Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy appeared in front of him as an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and committed another murder right before his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, I'll tell you about Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the daughter of the murdered couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Her whereabouts are currently unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mr. Messner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He made it all the way to Frankfurt, as ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.05,0:04:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He was recklessly stabbed two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.76,0:04:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He was involved in a drug deal that went bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when I was in the force,\NMessner was my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He was dismissed on drug charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:05:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who saved him after\Nthat incident was "The Baby."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He was an influential man in an extremist group.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an incident in Frankfurt where\Nfire was set to the Turkish quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The rumor is that the man behind it was "The Baby."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that a certain Asian\Nman put out the flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of that man was Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that... it was our Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said that the arson that\N"The Baby" was involved with
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,was a ceremony to welcome a certain man whom they\Nwere trying to make their organization's leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain man?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the name of the boy that Dr. Tenma saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of the man whom "The Baby" was\Ntrying to get as their leader... was Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's where you're going to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto... My life is just like that pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Is something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I got that one phone call, everything\Nin my life was a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My partner Messner and I had gotten our\Nhands dirty selling confiscated drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The person on the phone knew everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wanted him to keep quiet, I\Nhad to kill that married couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fortners in Heidelberg...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be safe if we killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There was another person in the house that night.\NHe was a newspaper reporter or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Messner and I killed all three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, we received a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was picked up by a syndicate\Nafter I quit the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I was immediately placed in a good position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The money I made was easily laundered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you met your wife and washed\Nyour hands clean of that business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why I was able to\Nleave the syndicate that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was on the phone that one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When we received all that money,\Nwho was controlling my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.15,0:08:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto, I'm grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always protected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then could you take back that last move?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're strict!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Buy me toys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Say goodbye to your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless. He's only thinking\Nabout toys right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto, has the detective called?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto, the detective's been hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the daughter of the couple\Nyou killed, Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who killed him was\Nyour bodyguard, Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it from the house next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be. Roberto is my\Nfriend. I can trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You... you've come to get your revenge on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto... Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking this bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to stay here, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A person like you has no one to trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mr. Mueller?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mueller?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Start the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been watching me from that\Nhouse for quite a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you enough to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I was blackmailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't kill your parents, they would\Nhave found out that I was selling drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Messner and I didn't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We had no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't... {\i1} have a choice{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They were wonderful people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother and father loved\Nme with all their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't even their real daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mom and Dad truly... truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite all of that, they were\Nkilled by scum like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbara...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Fritz...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbara... Fritz...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what it feels like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Fritz... He called me "Dad" for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found something I don't want to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbara... Fritz...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Düsseldorf... Every day at 8:30 at that café.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was ordered there every day after\NI joined the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was ordered to look very\Nclean-cut, just like a salaryman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day, a mother and her child would pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my only contact with everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hi there. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you hire that detective for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,To find you, Tenma, and my partner\Nfrom when I was a police officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but Messner is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was having a more detailed search done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a call from the detective last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something unusual for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Something unusual?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Messner was a heavy junkie who was in no condition\Nto get involved with some syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The killer wasn't from the Frankfurt syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's from Düsseldorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Düsseldorf?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you the details when I see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's scribbled on a piece of scrap paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Messner's case."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"The perpetrator."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who is Roberto?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the bag back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife and Fritz are relaxing right next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let my wife go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You should come back soon... to your "Happy Home."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you lend me your gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only use it at close range,\Nand it only has four bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to be careful so that I'll go\Nconfess to the police after this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. You'd better not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cover you from the house next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fritz?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Dad! It's a fishing rod.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid! He's not going to rest until\Nhe gets you to take him fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Roberto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of his friends from the security company\Nare here. It looks like something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't any damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto, Michael is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. There's just one broken window.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been some\Nkids in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where's the body...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The body of the detective that was here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There never was anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto... Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The madam and Fritz will be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now don't cause a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In truth, nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was a peaceful day,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and it will be from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a beautiful girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do with Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're treating her with courtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's quite special to a certain someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy's name was Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan, Johan, Johan! What's with this Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to live happily with\Nthe madam and Fritz.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patronage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do to Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Live happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, when are you going to take me fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, if it's sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see ghosts anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nice eyes. You and\NJohan look very much alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When can I see Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I came peacefully because you\Nsaid you'd let me meet Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.67,0:20:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to see you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He lives happily in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.47,0:20:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Munich...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You have really nice eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.15,0:20:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you. I used to be a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be at your house soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised Fritz I'd take\Nhim fishing tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it'll be sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.47,0:22:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll definitely be sunny.
